{"type": "article", "id": 10291, "title": "Shu Uemura 艺术家合作款限量洗发水系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-02T07:15:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235420z0djJYoIxagnNhpF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">日本彩妆品牌 Shu Uemura 每年都在世界各地和艺术家合作推出联名系列，今年他们和三位来自澳洲的艺术家联合推出了限量版的洗发水系列，三位艺术家分别是，时装设计师 Emma Mulholland，插画家 Andrew Archer 和纹身艺术家 Dean Carlyle，他们为 Shu Uemura 的洗发水外面上加入了丰富多彩的包装，把洗发水变成了艺术品。目前售价约 346 元人民币，将于本月正式发售。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235419Na5TWGEf6kmnlgYy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235420Kw9dER5oX7zmHUQO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}